title: vBulletin.Template - GameVB.diablo3 - SweetTorrents
description:
============================================================================================
Style Installation
============================================================================================

1) In the ZIP archive 

2) Upload all content in "UPLOAD" folder your main /forum/images directory

3) vB ACP -> Styles & Templates -> Download / Upload Styles -> Import Style XML File

 3i) Import DiabloIII-style-forum.xml first

If you have vBulletin Suite Version
 3ii) Import DiabloIII-style-blog.xml
 3iii) Import DiabloIII-style-cms.xml
